Package dmxeffects.dmx

Class Summary
ControlChannel Class linking specific channel values to specific actions.
DMXDisplay Class for providing the GUI elements of the DMX modules.
DMXInput  
DMXUserInput Class to get and validate input from a user.
Generator Class to generate DMX values for test purposes.
InputQueue Data structure to queue up input values of DMX for storage into the Universe.
Universe Class to store the values within a DMX Universe.
Validator Class to validate DMX channel numbers and values.
 

Exception Summary
InvalidChannelNumberException Exception to be thrown when a DMX Channel Number that is provided, is not valid.
InvalidChannelValueException Exception to be thrown when a DMX Channel Value that is provided, is not valid.
